rm-driven star formation to\na more locally driven, possibly sporadic form of star formation at mu_B~24, a\ntransition that does not appear to occur within LSB discs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2008 16:05:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
