 $p$ increases, which means that the\nsupport plays a harmful role in this case. Furthermore, $\\tilde{f}_{n,\\gamma}$\nis adaptive minimax up to a logarithmic term.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Oct 2008 06:49:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-10-30"}
