ture constant greater than about order unity. We argue that in this case a\nquantum effect, the Unruh-Wald quantum buoyancy, may protect the GSL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Oct 2008 11:53:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Dec 2008 11:57:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Feb 2009 10:25:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 26 May 2013 18:45:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-28"}
